    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0

    tmp = wp.sin(((v2 + 0.80 / tmp + 0.72) - wp.cos(v1 + 0.12)))
    tmp = wp.sin(((tmp + 0.84 / v0 + 0.30) * v1))
    v2 = v1
    tmp = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.78) * (tmp + 0.14 - tmp + 0.27)) + v2)
